rows.label: tlk00230101_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, don't you worry about me.
I'm fine.

rows.label: tlk00230101_msg0002
rows.name:
Ion's helping me look for
the thing I want to give you,
but no luck yet.

rows.label: tlk00230101_msg0003
rows.name:
I know it's a pain, but would you mind
coming back tomorrow? I bet it'll have
turned up by then.
